high_descs: Turn around and move to the microwave on the left.
Pick up the knife to your right.
Turn around and move around the island to the loaf of bread on the counter.
Slice the bread on the counter.
Turn to the right and move around the counter to the microwave.
Place the knife into the microwave.
Turn around and move around the island to the loaf of bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn to the right and move around the counter to the microwave.
Warm the bread in the microwave.
With the slice of bread, turn around and move to the fridge.
Place the slice of bread in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the end of the counter and turn towards the microwave.
Pick up the knife on the on the counter, to your right.
Turn around and go to the end of the counter, then turn right and go to the island on your right.
Cut the loaf of bread on the edge of the island into slices.
Turn to your right and go to the corner, then turn to your left and go to the microwave across from you.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the corner, then turn right and go back to the island on your right.
Pick up one of the slices of bread on the island.
Turn to your right and go to the corner, then turn to your left and go back to the microwave.
Place the slice of bread into the microwave, heat it up, then remove the slice of bread from the microwave.
Turn around and go to the corner, then turn to your left, and go to the refrigerator to your left.
Place the slice of bread on the top shelf of the refrigerator, in front of the white coffee cup.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in the microwave and a slice of bread in the refrigerator.
